_:N072d8b7f86624547a3931a1c5395b7f5 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Christian Wakeford was appointed Junior Lord of the Treasury (Government Whip) on 7 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously Assistant Whip, House of Commons between 10 July 2024 and 7 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was elected as the MP for Bury South in July 2024.</p>\n" .
